msgstr "验证证书链的末端证书。如果配置了末端证书的通用名称，则证书链末端证书的通用名称必须与之匹配。否则，除非已注册了一个或多个自定义的 `TokenCertificateValidator` 实现，否则该证书链的末端证书也必须存在于信任库中。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/security-oidc-bearer-token-authentication.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`quarkus.oidc.TokenCertificateValidator` can be used to add a custom certificate chain validation step. It can be used by all tenants expecting tokens with the certificate chain or bound to specific OIDC tenants with the `@quarkus.oidc.TenantFeature` annotation."
msgstr "`quarkus.oidc.TokenCertificateValidator` 可用于添加自定义证书链验证步骤。所有需要包含证书链的令牌的租户均可使用该组件，也可通过 `@quarkus.oidc.TenantFeature` 注解将其绑定到特定的 OIDC 租户。"

#. type: Plain text
