msgstr "link:https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc9449[RFC9449] 描述了一种“持有证明演示”（DPoP）机制，用于通过加密方式将访问令牌与当前客户端绑定，从而防止访问令牌丢失和重放攻击。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/security-oidc-bearer-token-authentication.adoc
#, fuzzy
