msgstr "link:https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc8705[RFC8705] 描述了一种将访问令牌与双向 TLS（mTLS）客户端身份验证证书进行绑定的机制。该机制要求客户端证书的 SHA256 指纹与 JWT 令牌或令牌内省确认 `x5t#S256` 证书的指纹相匹配。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/security-oidc-bearer-token-authentication.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For example, see https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc8705#section-3.1[JWT Certificate Thumbprint Confirmation Method] and https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc8705#section-3.2[Confirmation Method for Token Introspection] sections of https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc8705[RFC8705]."
msgstr "例如，请参阅 link:https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc8705[RFC 8705] 中的 link:https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc8705#section-3.1[“JWT 证书指纹确认方法] ”和 link:https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc8705#section-3.2[“令牌自检确认方法] ”章节。"

#. type: Plain text
